If there is indexing files or updating indexes, keep the cpp files as "Excluded"

if the Running devices is shwoing as "Loading Devices" 
     1) open a terminal in "D:\Android\SDK\platform-tools"
     2) taskkill /F /IM adb.exe
     3) adb start-server
     4) adb kill-server
     5) PS D:\Android\SDK\platform-tools> adb start-server
        * daemon not running; starting now at tcp:5037
        * daemon started successfully
        PS D:\Android\SDK\platform-tools>

    woala, the adb will restart and the Running devices will show the devices.
